high_descs: Walk into a break room and stand between the two diningtables.
Pick up the fork from the circular table.
Walk back into the home office you were just in, and face the bowl.
Put the fork in the gray bowl in front of you.
Pick up the gray bowl.
Go back into the diningtable.
Put the gray bowl down on the diningtable, close to both armchairs.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a bowl on a round dining table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the fork from the table.
Turn around and go to the bowl in the study room.
Put the fork in the bowl on the table.
Take the bowl with fork from the table.
Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Put the bowl with fork on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the Fork with Bowl on the DiningTable.

high_descs: Turn left and exit this room, then go into the door just ahead, going to the circular table ahead.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Go back to the room you started in and go to the desk in the corner to the right of the entrance.
Put the fork inside the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl with the fork in it.
Go back to the table you got the fork from.
Place the bowl down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a fork in it on a dining table.
